{
  "stem": "23645.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would-- so-- a little bit on a big pot that's left over, you know, you start taking it out, it's quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was very, very, very sustaining and probably instrumental in-- in keeping me alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were all kinds of conversations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were conversations in the camp when we went to sleep, after they-- there was a bulb [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they say 'lights out,' you know, you think somebody went up there and unscrewed the bulb.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes we didn't even want to do this, because then you have all these bugs descending on it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So sometimes we even left the lights on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there were these groups of people, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were-- they come from all walks of life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were artists.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were teachers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were, you know, writers and poets, doctors, lawyers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they would philosophy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I particularly remember a certain conversation. .",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember hearing, anybody that will be lucky enough to survive this [BACKROUND NOISE] nightmare, this-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] will live in paradise.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There will be just absolutely beautiful life, a beauti-- hunger will completely disappear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There will not be any hunger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People will be kind to one another.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There will be no discrimination as we know it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It'll be pure paradise.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember thinking, I want to survive this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I want to live in this kind of paradise.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Particularly what attracted me is that nobody's going to be hungry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There's going to be plenty of food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Unfortunately, you know, as we know, you turn on the television and there is still-- you see Biafra.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You still see ethnic cleansing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, as a survivor, you know, I-- I identify with this kid behind barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it made me furious, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
